\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b a}) Subsp.{\b  rotundifolia} (incl.{\i  S. heucherifolia} Griseb. & Schenk,{\i  S. lasiophylla} Schott, {\i S. repanda} auct., vix Willd.): Petiole narrow right up to junction with lamina. Lamina with a narrow cartilaginous border. 2n = 22. Almost throughout the range of the species, but rare in the extreme south.
